         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Note of hand. I, Herakles son of Akousilaos, Macedonian of the catoecic cavalry, to Akousilaos son of Akousilaos my younger brother, greeting. I swear by Caesar son of God and Imperator, that I will truly abide by and perform all that pertains to the two shares out of five shares and will divide ...</ab>
